processingCommand.script:
IF "${ImportFileName}"=="" GOTO IMPORT
SET ImportFileArgument=-i ${ImportFileName}
set ImportThreadParameter=""
IF "${ImportThreads}" NEQ "" set ImportThreadParameter=-t ${ImportThreads}
:IMPORT
Echo on
IF "${ImportThreads}" NEQ "" (
   ${XT_RABO_TASKPROCESSOR} ${ImportTDFName} %ImportFileArgument% %ImportThreadParameter% /S
) ELSE (
   ${XT_RABO_TASKPROCESSOR} ${ImportTDFName} %ImportFileArgument% /S
)
Echo off
set retcode=%errorlevel%
echo TaskProcessor ended with return code: %retcode%
IF %retcode% EQU 0 GOTO NORMALFLOW
GOTO ERRORFLOW
:NORMALFLOW
set resexe=0
GOTO END
:ERRORFLOW
set resexe=1
GOTO END
:END
exit %resexe%
